425
00:25:14.800 --> 00:25:16.367
Tak Soo, i-compile mo ito at i-report mo sa akin.

426
00:25:16.367 --> 00:25:17.700
Naintindihan.

427
00:25:17.700 --> 00:25:18.733
At...

428
00:25:18.733 --> 00:25:20.267
